Alan Oppenheimer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alan_Oppenheimer 0 Alan Louis Oppenheimer (born April 23, 1930) is an American actor and voice actor. He has performed numerous roles on live-action television since the 1960s, and has had an active career doing voice work in cartoons since the 1970s.
